AboutForm_Description:
Sawubona lapho!

Ngethemba ukuthi uyalujabulela lolu hlelo kuze kube manje. Ngenze lolu hlelo njengobufakazi bomqondo
 ngokudala ubuciko be-pixel obusezingeni eliphezulu. Lolu hlelo lunikeza izinketho ezimbalwa zokubuka ukusiza
empeleni wakha ubuciko kugeyimu. Futhi ungagcina ku-PNG noma kufomethi ye-Schematic.
Okubaluleke kakhulu. ungasebenzisa imodi ye-double-layer, ehlanganisa ingilazi enemibala
amaphaneli anamabhulokhi e-Minecraft amasha ukuze akhe iphalethi yombala enkulu nakakhulu.

Ngezansi lezi izixhumanisi ezimbalwa ongazithola ziwusizo.  Zihlole uma uthola a
ithuba. 

Taylor Love
Aka Pangama
ColorReducer_Algorithm_Tooltip: Ukwandiswa kombala kunciphisa inani lemibala ehlukile yesithombe kuyilapho kugcina isithombe esisha sibukeka sifana nesokuqala. Kukhona ama-algorithms amaningi ahlukene. Khetha i-algorithm oyikhonzile futhi uyisebenzise.
ColorReducer_ColorCache_Tooltip:
Funda kabanzi ngakho ngokuningiliziwe lapha:
https://www.codeproject.com/Articles/66341/A-Simple-Yet-Quite-Powerful-Palette-Quantizer-in-C

Ibanga le-Euclidian: Lihamba kancane kodwa linembile
I-hashing ezwelayo endaweni: Ngokushesha
I-Octree: Kuyashesha futhi kunembile
ColorReducer_ColorCount_Tooltip: I-quantizer izonciphisa inani lemibala ibe inombolo engu-256 noma ngaphansi.
ColorReducer_Dither_Tooltip: Izitayela eziningi ezahlukene ongakhetha kuzo. Ngokwami ngicabanga ukuthi i-bayer dithering ibukeka ingcono kakhulu.
ColorReducer_Instructions_Tooltip: Ubuciko obunemibala eminingi eyingqayizivele buzothatha isikhathi esiningi ukwakha. Unganciphisa inani eliphelele lemibala ehlukile ngaphambi kokuthi uqale inqubo yokunikezela. Chofoza izihloko zombhalo omnyama ukuze uthole ulwazi olwengeziwe.
ColorReducer_Parallel_Tooltip: Inani lezinqubo ezizosebenza ngokuhambisana. Ukusebenzisa izinombolo eziphakeme kungasheshisa inqubo yokulinganisa.
ColorReducer_RgbBucketSize_Tooltip:
Sheshisa ukunikezwa ngokunciphisa inani lemibala ehlukile. Esikhundleni semibala ehlukile engu-255^3, unganciphisa inani lemibala ehlukile 51^3. 

Okushesha kakhulu: 5^3
Okunembe kakhulu: 255^3

Isibalo:
F(X) => Amaminithi(255, Umjikelezo(X/5, 0) * 5)

Isibonelo:
Uma usayizi wengcezu ingu-5 (51^3 imibala):
f(255) => 255
f(254) => 255
f(251) => 250
ErrorSender_IncludeImage: Ingabe uzimisele ukulayisha isithombe sakho samanje ukuze sihlaziywe? (Ongakukhetha)
ErrorSender_SendMeSomeInfo:
Ingabe uzimisele ukungithumelela ulwazi oluthile ukuze ungisize ngilungise leli phutha?
Uma kunjalo, ulwazi olulandelayo luzozip. Bese ungathumela ulwazi ku 
mina njenge
ErrorSender_Yes: Yebo! Zip ulwazi oluthile ukuze udaba lulungiswe.
Error_CannotExceedWorldHeight_0: I-Minecraft ayikwazi ukusekela izithombe ezinkulu kunamabhulokhi angu-{0} ngobude.
Error_GlassRequiredForMultiLayer: Okungenani into eyodwa yengilazi kufanele ivulwe uma ukhetha ukudinga izendlalelo eziningi.
Error_ImageTooLarge: Isithombe sakho sikhulu kakhulu ukuthi singasetshenzwa.
Error_NeedMoreRam: Ayikho inkumbulo eyanele. Sicela uzame futhi noma wehlise usayizi wesithombe uma inkinga iqhubeka.
Error_NonGlassRequired: Okungenani into eyodwa engeyona ingilazi kufanele ikhethwe.
Error_OneMaterialRequired: Okungenani into eyodwa kufanele inikwe amandla ngaso sonke isikhathi.
OtherOptions_ConfirmFactoryReset: Ingabe uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukusetha kabusha zonke izinketho ze-PixelStacker zibuyele kuzilungiselelo ezizenzakalelayo? Kubandakanya izinto, osayizi, izifunda zokubuka, izinketho zokunikezela, njll.
OtherOptions_Instructions: Faka ububanzi obukhulu noma ubude obukhulu ukuze ukhawulele usayizi wokuphumayo.
PreRenderOptions_Algorithm_Tooltip:
Ama-algorithms ahlukene asebenzisa amasu ahlukene 
ukuhlanganisa imibala ndawonye. Abanye basebenzisa amabhakede anombala,
abanye basebenzisa ibanga lendawo emibaleni eseduze. Zama
bonke bese unquma ukuthi iyiphi oyithandayo.
PreRenderOptions_ColorCacheSize_Tooltip:
Amanani amancane ayashesha kodwa anembe kancane.
Amanani aphezulu anensa kodwa anembe kakhulu.
PreRenderOptions_Dither_Tooltip:
Abanye abantu bathanda ukuphefumula.
angifuni. Angilokothi ngikwenze. ngiyazonda 
ukwehla. Kodwa hey - uyakwenza.
PreRenderOptions_Parallel_Tooltip:
Sheshisa inqubo ye-quantizing ngokuthatha
inzuzo ye-multicore CPU. 

Amanani aphansi = azinzile
Amanani aphezulu = ngokushesha
Amanani aphezulu kakhulu = amaphutha angenzeka
